flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[User selects an active raffle]
    B --> C[Purchase view is displayed: Payment methods, ticket quantity input, and user form]
    C --> D[User fills out the form]
    D --> D1[Form fields:
- National ID
- Full name
- Email
- Phone/Whatsapp
- Bank transfer screenshot
- Bank reference number
- Number of tickets
]
    D1 --> E[User submits form after making manual payment]
    E --> F[System saves data and sets status to In Process]
    F --> G[Admin manually verifies payment]

    G -->|Valid payment| H[Randomly assign available ticket numbers]
    H --> I[User is notified via Email and Whatsapp]
    I --> J[End: Purchase confirmed]

    G -->|Invalid payment or error| K[Admin rejects the purchase]
    K --> L[User is notified of rejection]
    L --> M[End: Purchase rejected]
